I would say the DNA
was a magic wand for me.

00:59:09.000 --> 00:59:13.000
It's a magic wand
for any innocent man,

00:59:13.000 --> 00:59:18.000
but it'll be your
damning thing if you did it

00:59:18.000 --> 00:59:21.000
and, uh, that's what we need.

00:59:21.000 --> 00:59:24.000
And it's...
it's almost like, um,

00:59:24.000 --> 00:59:28.000
some sort of superhero
type of element

00:59:28.000 --> 00:59:30.000
that we have in society

00:59:30.000 --> 00:59:33.000
and without it,
I would still be there.

00:59:33.000 --> 00:59:36.000
To be a free man,
a free, innocent person

00:59:36.000 --> 00:59:38.000
and, uh, just to be
a regular guy

00:59:38.000 --> 00:59:44.000
is, uh, more joy than
